I will be removing any other replies to this thread. I intend for it to be read-only. If you wish to discuss a collateral, post it in the appropriate application thread. This thread will be updated at least once every week (on Mondays.) Note: Please refer to the new Collateral Status Index post for the new updates. This CSI Post is now deprecated. But I think the order in the list does not quite reflect the “on-work” RWA collaterals we’re doing at the moment, and the ones likely upcoming. At the moment (to be on-boarded) are: CF-DROP, FF1-DROP, HTC-DROP and P1-DROP.

Hi, @williamr  I’ve moved those assets to the top of the table and marked them as In Progress. As for future status changes, please let me know in case I miss something or feel free to edit the post yourself. The message I’m replying to can be safely deleted (we’re trying to keep the thread read-only). DM me if I can provide additional help
